    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel is coming for CEYPETCO",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy Minister Kanjana Wijesekara said that the ship carrying 40,000 metric tons of diesel purchased by CEYPETCO will arrive in Sri Lanka on July 8 or 9.",
        "Petrol will arrive between 11-14 July and 22-23 July.",
        "Another batch of diesel is expected between July 22-23, he added.",
        "He said the above during the press conference held today (03) in Colombo."
      ],
